dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Whitewater quadrangle, Riverside County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle WHITEWATER, CA 1955, AMS 2651 I NW -- Series V895, PHOTOREVISED 1988." "First printing, August 2004." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. "Donald D. Clarke Honorary Map." Includes "pertinent references."
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
